  "texts": [
    "Certain types of projects where there are penalties for late completion or where specific deadlines must be met place greater emphasis on tardiness.",
    "Additionally, tardiness is closely related to both completion time and cost, as it takes both the duration of the project and any penalties for late completion into account.",
    "In many situations, minimizing completion time or cost may also result in a reduction in tardiness.",
    "Therefore, it makes sense that researchers place more emphasis on these objectives as opposed to tardiness specifically.",
    "Furthermore, tardiness could be used in some situations as a constraint in lieu of a performance measure."
  ],
